data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite and modern 4-bedroom, 2-bath house is nestled in the serene community of Villa Mar, offering both comfort and convenience. Built in 2021, this contemporary residence spans 1,730 square feet, providing ample space for you and your loved ones. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the charm of luxury vinyl flooring throughout, offering both durability and an elegant touch. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The kitchen boasts a walk-in pantry, ensuring you have all the storage you need to keep your culinary essentials organized. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a spacious laundry room, and the kitchen is equipped with modern appliances for added convenience. The master bedroom is a true oasis with its en-suite bathroom, featuring double vanities, a luxurious tub, and a separate shower. This retreat allows you to unwind and indulge in tranquility after a long day. The other three bedrooms are generously sized, offering flexibility for guest rooms, home offices, or playrooms. One of the highlights of this home is the screened-in patio, where you can enjoy the fresh air and scenic views without any pesky insects disrupting your relaxation. Additionally, the two-car garage ensures plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage needs. Within the community, you'll have access to fantastic amenities, including a sparkling swimming pool, perfect for cooling off during warm summer days, and a fun-filled playground for children to enjoy. This home's modern features, coupled with its convenient location and community amenities, make it an unparalleled living experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning house your forever home! Schedule a viewing today and be prepared to fall in love with the epitome of comfort and luxury.
